<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>World Population Report</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>World Population Report</h1>
        <p>Global Population Overview</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">

        <!-- Summary Section -->
        <section class="card">
            <h2>Population Summary</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Total World Population: <strong>8.1 Billion</strong></li>
                <li>Most Populous Country: <strong>India</strong></li>
                <li>Least Populous Country: <strong>Vatican City</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Table Section -->
        <section class="card">
            <h2>Top 5 Most Populated Countries</h2>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Rank</th>
                    <th>Country</th>
                    <th>Population</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td>India</td>
                    <td>1.43 B</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>2</td>
                    <td>China</td>
                    <td>1.42 B</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>3</td>
                    <td>USA</td>
                    <td>339 M</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>4</td>
                    <td>Indonesia</td>
                    <td>277 M</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>5</td>
                    <td>Pakistan</td>
                    <td>241 M</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </section>

        <!-- Conclusion -->
        <section class="card">
            <h2>Conclusion</h2>
            <p>
                The world population continues to grow rapidly, with Asia contributing
                the largest share. Population trends impact economy, resources, and
                global development.
            </p>
        </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>Prepared by: Your Name | Year: 2025</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
